43), 1943-1946."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:06.216Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-13", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-13"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn85042243/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [46.826465, -100.88974], "location": ["bismarck", "morton", "mandan", "north dakota", "united states", "burleigh"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-100.88974, 46.826465], "number": ["microfilm master", "6529", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn85042243/1937-12-31/ed-1/", "2330-5967", "online resource", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn85042243/1916-11-21/ed-1/", "1", "microfilm service copy", "chicago hist soc libr", "sn85042242", "library of congress", "sn89074367", "2026-04-08t10:47:12.200000", "11987205", "original", "kansas state hist soc, newsp proj", "sn85042588", "state hist soc of n dakota", "state hist soc of missouri", "sn85042243", "2023-08-22t07:32:24.084270", "western rsv hist soc, newsp proj", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Bismarck daily tribune", "Bismarck evening tribune"], "partof": ["the bismarck tribune (bismarck, n.d.) 1916-current", "catalog", "chronicling america", "serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 91.58265, "shelf_id": "Newspaper", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["newspapers", "bismarck", "morton", "mandan", "bismarck (n.d.)", "north dakota", "united states", "burleigh"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:15:53.161Z", "title": "The Bismarck tribune", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn85042243/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2013218926/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1916", "dates": ["[1916 TO 9999]"], "description": ["Daily, <1982>- Began with thirty-sixth year, no. 281 (November 21, 1916). Sometimes published a morning edition and Sunday edition. \"Official newspaper for Bismarck and Mandan, N.D.\" Volume numbering irregular. Weekly ed.: Bismarck weekly tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1884), 1916-1943. Monthly ed.: Bismarck tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1943), 1943-1946. Thirty-sixth year, no. 281 (November 21, 1916); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 21, 2013). December 30, 1922 (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 21, 2013)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:05.616Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2013218926/", "image_url": [], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["bismarck", "morton", "mandan", "north dakota", "united states", "burleigh"], "number": ["2013218926", "online resource", "2330-5975", "2013218925", "244293920", "2013218928", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Bismarck daily tribune", "Bismarck evening tribune"], "partof": ["the bismarck tribune (bismarck, north dakota) 1916-current [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 82.407906, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "bismarck", "morton", "periodicals", "mandan", "bismarck (n.d.)", "north dakota", "electronic journals", "united states", "burleigh"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:48:24.858Z", "title": "The Bismarck tribune", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2013218926/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2018218966/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1906", "dates": ["[1906 TO 9999]"], "description": ["Weekly Began in 1906. \"Beiblatt zu der Pierce County tribune.\" Place of publication varies: <1906>-Nov. 23, 1911, Rugby, N.D.; Dec. 7, 1911-Apr. 25, 1912, Devils Lake, N.D.; May 2, 1912-July 13, 1945?, Bismarck, N.D.; <Nov. 27, 1945>-, with an office in Bismarck, which moved to Fredonia, N.D. <Feb. 9, 1968>. Description based on: 1. Jahrgang, no. 37 (11. April, 1907); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed October 3, 2018). Latest issue consulted: 15. Jahrgang, no. 27 (19. Oktober 1920) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed October 3, 2018)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:44.751Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2018218966/", "image_url": [], "index": 6, "language": ["german"], "location": ["omaha", "bismarck", "douglas", "logan", "north dakota", "fredonia", "nebraska", "devils lake", "pierce", "ramsey", "united states", "burleigh", "rugby"], "number": ["online resource", "1055488809", "2018218966", "2639-5150", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["der staats=anzeiger (rugby, north dakota) 1906-current [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 51.817974, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "omaha", "bismarck (n.d.)", "bismarck", "douglas", "logan", "fredonia", "devils lake (n.d.)", "rugby (n.d.)", "nebraska", "devils lake", "pierce", "fredonia (n.d.)", "north dakota", "ramsey", "united states", "burleigh", "rugby"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:56:24.792Z", "title": "Der Staats=Anzeiger", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2018218966/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2013218923/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1875", "dates": ["[1875 TO 1881]"], "description": ["Triweekly Began with November 15, 1875 issue. Ceased with April 16, 1881 issue? Weekly eds.: Bismarck weekly tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1875), 1875-1878, and: Bismarck tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1878), 1878-1881. Desc